WEBVTT

01:30.920 --> 01:35.020
[Dream of Golden Years]

01:35.810 --> 01:39.520
[2020]

01:51.710 --> 01:53.560
Happy New Year, Xiaolan.

01:58.920 --> 02:00.730
Happy New Year, Auntie.

02:08.139 --> 02:09.550
The colorful neon lights

02:10.470 --> 02:12.470
illuminate the gatherings of some,

02:13.030 --> 02:14.830
the hustle and bustle of others,

02:15.580 --> 02:18.180
and the drifting of those away from home.

02:18.010 --> 02:21.340
[Episode 25 The Outsider]

02:29.000 --> 02:29.590
Cheng.

02:30.910 --> 02:31.750
I feel like...

02:32.360 --> 02:33.240
I might have really

02:33.240 --> 02:34.280
fallen for You Li.

02:34.560 --> 02:35.220
Might have?

02:36.400 --> 02:36.960
You don't know

02:36.960 --> 02:38.020
your own feelings?

02:39.500 --> 02:40.450
Or do you think

02:41.280 --> 02:42.280
you just pity her?

02:43.150 --> 02:44.960
I do pity her a little.

02:46.079 --> 02:47.610
But it's not entirely pity.

02:49.240 --> 02:50.240
It's more like...

02:51.310 --> 02:52.040
Admiration?

02:52.430 --> 02:53.160
Admiration?

02:54.280 --> 02:55.340
That word might not be

02:55.340 --> 02:56.470
entirely accurate.

02:57.120 --> 02:58.400
I just feel that

02:58.840 --> 02:59.960
she's had it really tough.

02:59.960 --> 03:01.490
Look at how hard her life is.

03:01.520 --> 03:02.840
Yet she still maintains her conscience,

03:02.840 --> 03:03.910
relies on herself,

03:03.930 --> 03:04.870
and works hard in life.

03:04.870 --> 03:06.200
I think that's amazing.

03:06.360 --> 03:07.360
If it were me,

03:07.430 --> 03:10.230
I probably couldn't have
accomplished anything.

03:11.560 --> 03:12.680
Oh, Wei.

03:13.080 --> 03:15.940
You're really feeling
the first stirrings of love.

03:17.280 --> 03:18.360
When I first met

03:18.360 --> 03:19.280
Xiaolan,

03:19.800 --> 03:20.860
I felt the same way.

03:22.560 --> 03:24.000
I just hope You Li and I

03:24.150 --> 03:25.800
can be like you and Xiaolan,

03:25.820 --> 03:27.150
and have a happy ending.

03:30.800 --> 03:31.400
Wei,

03:33.000 --> 03:34.710
have you noticed that Xiaolan

03:35.150 --> 03:37.210
has been acting differently lately?

03:37.240 --> 03:38.040
Differently?

03:39.280 --> 03:39.800
No.

03:40.030 --> 03:41.360
She's still as beautiful

03:41.360 --> 03:42.490
and capable as ever.

03:44.960 --> 03:46.820
I just feel that something is off.

03:47.800 --> 03:50.079
She seems to have a lot on her mind.

03:51.030 --> 03:52.560
But she also seems anxious,

03:52.910 --> 03:55.310
like she's desperately racing against time.

03:55.310 --> 03:56.240
Sometimes,

03:57.340 --> 03:59.240
it's like she's a different person.

03:59.240 --> 04:00.590
Her reactions become slow,

04:00.590 --> 04:02.720
like she has forgotten a lot of things.

04:03.430 --> 04:05.160
But she keeps trying to hide it.

04:05.190 --> 04:06.790
I didn't want to pry, either.

04:07.420 --> 04:08.280
I think

04:08.280 --> 04:09.940
you're just overthinking it.

04:10.000 --> 04:10.910
Xiaolan has always been

04:10.910 --> 04:12.710
a busy person with a short memory.

04:12.710 --> 04:13.560
With so much going on,

04:13.560 --> 04:15.190
it's normal to forget things.

04:15.190 --> 04:15.960
Besides,

04:16.160 --> 04:17.360
time waits for no one.

04:17.480 --> 04:19.540
Of course she has to seize the moment.

04:19.680 --> 04:20.390
Especially you.

04:20.390 --> 04:21.120
You need to seize the moment, too.

04:21.120 --> 04:22.070
You need to hold on to Xiaolan.

04:22.070 --> 04:23.040
Hurry up and get the marriage license.

04:23.040 --> 04:24.300
Be my brother-in-law.

04:24.790 --> 04:25.270
Okay.

04:26.640 --> 04:27.170
Yes, sir.

04:28.360 --> 04:29.090
Comrade Xia.

04:29.870 --> 04:31.600
You and the Young Master are...

04:32.000 --> 04:33.460
We are business partners.

04:33.680 --> 04:34.810
I'm his consultant.

04:37.080 --> 04:37.990
I saw you with

04:38.010 --> 04:40.310
the Du family's Second Young Master today.

04:40.310 --> 04:40.800
Yes.

04:41.390 --> 04:43.120
I'm his special assistant now.

04:44.000 --> 04:45.040
I never expected that

04:45.040 --> 04:46.040
when we met again,

04:46.360 --> 04:46.870
we would be

04:46.870 --> 04:47.930
in opposing camps.

04:51.880 --> 04:52.610
Comrade Xia,

04:53.440 --> 04:55.040
I know this is presumptuous,

04:55.680 --> 04:56.310
but

04:57.920 --> 05:00.250
could you let the Second Young Master win?

05:00.430 --> 05:01.600
I need this job.

05:02.560 --> 05:03.420
I want revenge.

05:05.630 --> 05:06.870
Actually, when I met you

05:06.870 --> 05:08.070
on the train that day,

05:08.360 --> 05:09.390
I had just escaped

05:09.390 --> 05:10.680
from my ex-husband's home.

05:10.680 --> 05:11.720
To divorce me

05:11.720 --> 05:13.120
and marry another woman,

05:13.190 --> 05:15.050
he cheated me out of all my assets.

05:15.510 --> 05:17.970
He even tricked me into
getting an abortion.

05:18.360 --> 05:19.240
It was a 5-month-old,

05:19.240 --> 05:20.480
fully formed baby.

05:22.010 --> 05:22.560
Even when I was

05:22.560 --> 05:24.360
recovering from the procedure,

05:24.390 --> 05:26.240
he wouldn't give me any food.

05:26.970 --> 05:29.170
Wasn't he trying to drive me to my death?

05:29.560 --> 05:30.750
I had no choice but to flee onto the train

05:30.750 --> 05:31.720
penniless,

05:32.040 --> 05:33.190
and that was when I met you.

05:33.190 --> 05:34.390
If it weren't for you,

05:34.750 --> 05:36.150
I wouldn't be here today.

05:37.390 --> 05:38.120
Comrade Xia,

05:38.630 --> 05:39.070
I know

05:39.070 --> 05:40.730
how pathetic I look right now.

05:40.950 --> 05:42.350
But I'm filled with hate.

05:43.720 --> 05:44.580
I want revenge.

05:45.240 --> 05:46.120
I need money.

05:48.120 --> 05:49.920
When I met you on the train,

05:50.430 --> 05:51.240
I guessed you had been through

05:51.240 --> 05:52.640
something unspeakable.

05:53.560 --> 05:54.600
I lent you money

05:55.270 --> 05:56.270
because I wanted to give you

05:56.270 --> 05:57.270
some hope to go on.

05:58.159 --> 05:59.600
When I first saw you today,

05:59.600 --> 06:01.480
I was actually quite happy for you.

06:01.480 --> 06:03.480
You look much more presentable now.

06:04.720 --> 06:06.050
But I didn't expect that

06:06.360 --> 06:08.030
while you gained this appearance,

06:08.030 --> 06:09.430
you lost your integrity.

06:10.750 --> 06:11.310
You say that you

06:11.310 --> 06:12.970
can't afford to lose this job.

06:13.510 --> 06:15.070
But have you ever thought about

06:15.070 --> 06:16.070
what I would lose?

06:20.310 --> 06:21.190
Actually, I knew that

06:21.190 --> 06:22.650
this would be your answer.

06:23.700 --> 06:24.430
Comrade Xia,

06:25.040 --> 06:26.500
if I've disappointed you,

06:27.070 --> 06:28.000
I am truly sorry.

06:29.240 --> 06:30.900
I won't bother you any longer.

06:42.950 --> 06:43.920
Is Ye Xiaoqiong really that miserable

06:43.920 --> 06:44.920
and desperate for money?

06:44.920 --> 06:45.870
Why not just buy her off

06:45.870 --> 06:46.600
to be our spy?

06:47.159 --> 06:48.720
She has changed, yes.

06:49.190 --> 06:50.360
But she wouldn't go so far as

06:50.360 --> 06:51.820
to sell her soul for money.

06:51.870 --> 06:53.130
You admire her so much.

06:54.040 --> 06:55.470
You won't go easy on Du Zhaoji

06:55.470 --> 06:57.200
out of sympathy for her, right?

06:58.430 --> 06:59.870
If you say that again,

07:00.120 --> 07:01.520
our partnership is over.

07:01.950 --> 07:02.630
You're so sensitive.

07:02.630 --> 07:03.950
I didn't really say anything.

07:03.950 --> 07:04.800
Did you set up an appointment

07:04.800 --> 07:05.800
with the property consultant yet?

07:05.800 --> 07:06.510
It's all set.

07:06.510 --> 07:07.830
You can meet him tomorrow.

07:07.830 --> 07:08.560
Okay. Bye.

07:09.180 --> 07:10.980
Where are you going? Wait for me.

07:14.870 --> 07:16.130
Aren't you going back?

07:16.310 --> 07:17.750
I have to ensure your safety.

07:17.750 --> 07:18.680
This is Gangdao.

07:18.750 --> 07:20.870
Someone might actually want to kill you.

07:20.870 --> 07:21.310
Who?

07:21.630 --> 07:22.310
Xia Ziyu?

07:24.160 --> 07:25.360
Do you want to see her?

07:25.750 --> 07:26.280
Get lost.

07:59.510 --> 08:00.070
Are you

08:00.070 --> 08:01.430
hiding something from me?

08:01.430 --> 08:02.040
No.

08:14.830 --> 08:15.430
Granny Yu.

08:15.630 --> 08:16.760
You're still awake?

08:17.830 --> 08:19.190
Xiaolan isn't back yet?

08:20.120 --> 08:22.040
She went on a last-minute
business trip to Gangdao.

08:22.040 --> 08:23.640
She should be back tomorrow.

08:23.800 --> 08:25.390
Don't worry. Get some rest.

08:36.840 --> 08:37.240
Okay.

08:37.480 --> 08:38.270
I agree

08:38.600 --> 08:39.530
to go take a look.

08:40.360 --> 08:40.870
But

08:41.240 --> 08:42.770
I will only speak the truth.

08:43.080 --> 08:43.909
If

08:43.909 --> 08:45.540
I say something you don't like,

08:45.540 --> 08:47.340
you'll have to bear it yourself.

08:47.670 --> 08:49.200
I'm telling you this upfront

08:49.200 --> 08:51.030
so it won't be awkward later.

08:52.240 --> 08:54.030
I'm already very grateful that

08:54.240 --> 08:55.620
you've agreed to take a look, Mr. Wu.

08:55.620 --> 08:56.240
If there really are

08:56.240 --> 08:57.240
any problems,

08:57.270 --> 08:58.080
we certainly wouldn't dare

08:58.080 --> 08:59.010
to build rashly.

08:59.670 --> 09:01.400
When the foundation is nearly done,

09:01.400 --> 09:03.550
I'll send someone to Gangdao
to pick you up.

09:03.550 --> 09:04.000
Okay.

09:05.480 --> 09:06.200
I'll see you out.

09:06.200 --> 09:06.660
No need.

09:09.750 --> 09:11.510
Mr. Wu's matter is settled.

09:11.910 --> 09:13.840
Now we just need to wait for Mr. Qiu.

09:39.870 --> 09:41.080
I didn't expect you and Xia Xiaolan

09:41.080 --> 09:43.010
to have this kind of relationship.

09:46.270 --> 09:48.030
I'm sorry, Second Young Master.

09:48.030 --> 09:49.090
I didn't lie to you.

09:50.630 --> 09:51.690
Before yesterday,

09:51.800 --> 09:53.470
I had only met her once.

09:54.030 --> 09:55.030
We weren't close.

09:55.270 --> 09:56.270
After yesterday,

09:56.790 --> 09:57.510
we're even less likely

09:57.510 --> 09:59.370
to have any kind of relationship.

10:01.160 --> 10:02.890
You'd better not be lying to me.

10:05.480 --> 10:06.320
Think about

10:06.830 --> 10:08.630
who you're relying on

10:08.790 --> 10:10.190
for the life you have now,

10:11.090 --> 10:12.820
and whose side you should be on.

10:15.440 --> 10:16.640
Second Young Master,

10:16.960 --> 10:18.080
I am very aware.

10:25.670 --> 10:26.670
Shengcheng.

10:32.670 --> 10:33.550
If we get Mr. Qiu

10:33.550 --> 10:34.870
to go back to Shengcheng with us,

10:34.870 --> 10:36.530
there might actually be a way.

10:40.320 --> 10:41.720
Be careful.

10:44.000 --> 10:44.600
What?

10:45.220 --> 10:46.930
[With vengeance unfulfilled,
I'm too ashamed to return home.]

10:46.480 --> 10:47.010
Let's go.

10:47.240 --> 10:48.840
Mr. Qiu won't go back with me.

10:53.840 --> 10:55.390
Once you pass the checkpoint safely,

10:55.390 --> 10:56.920
everything should be fine.

10:57.030 --> 10:57.720
This is...

10:58.240 --> 10:59.150
Since I'm here,

10:59.320 --> 11:00.220
I might as well go back

11:00.220 --> 11:01.550
and play the filial son.

11:02.320 --> 11:02.790
Thanks.

11:13.790 --> 11:16.640
♪ Drifting with the wind and waves ♪

11:15.170 --> 11:16.500
Gangdao and Shengcheng

11:16.870 --> 11:18.120
are separated by only a strip of water,

11:17.600 --> 11:20.440
♪ Drifting with the waves of life ♪

11:18.510 --> 11:20.440
yet they are two different worlds.

11:20.870 --> 11:22.360
Those who abandoned their old identities

11:21.790 --> 11:24.990
♪ The moment our paths crossed ♪

11:22.360 --> 11:23.630
and ended up here,

11:24.000 --> 11:25.150
willing or not,

11:25.740 --> 11:28.850
♪ We were instantly worlds apart ♪

11:26.240 --> 11:28.040
will surely return home one day.

11:29.150 --> 11:30.240
Will I, too,

11:29.800 --> 11:32.680
♪ Fate drifts with the wind ♪

11:30.670 --> 11:32.870
eventually return to where I came from?

11:33.740 --> 11:36.690
♪ Watching over you even if fate ends ♪

11:34.670 --> 11:35.870
Miss, here is your ID.

11:36.390 --> 11:36.990
Thank you.

11:37.650 --> 11:41.270
♪ The moment we gazed at each other ♪

11:41.590 --> 11:45.110
♪ Tears fell in my heart ♪

11:52.780 --> 11:54.580
What were you doing at the hotel?

11:55.150 --> 11:56.080
How did you know Xia Xiaolan

11:56.080 --> 11:57.010
came to Gangdao?

11:57.270 --> 11:58.360
Are you the one

11:58.750 --> 12:00.680
making trouble behind the scenes?

12:03.240 --> 12:04.040
Young Master,

12:05.000 --> 12:06.120
if my face

12:06.120 --> 12:07.250
gets bruised later,

12:08.240 --> 12:10.240
how should I explain it to Mr. Du?

12:18.720 --> 12:19.270
As for your affairs, Young Master,

12:19.270 --> 12:21.200
Mr. Du naturally knows about them.

12:21.510 --> 12:23.040
He mentioned it in passing,

12:23.280 --> 12:25.010
and I just happened to find out.

12:26.150 --> 12:27.480
It'd better be the case.

12:28.320 --> 12:29.450
Don't let me find out

12:29.750 --> 12:30.600
that you deliberately lured

12:30.600 --> 12:31.600
Xia Xiaolan here.

12:32.720 --> 12:34.630
Why the big reaction?

12:35.840 --> 12:36.440
So worried

12:36.440 --> 12:38.040
about Xia Xiaolan's safety?

12:38.750 --> 12:39.600
But I seem to recall that

12:39.600 --> 12:41.240
she has a boyfriend.

12:42.200 --> 12:43.260
Come to think of it,

12:43.350 --> 12:44.350
I've even met him.

12:44.680 --> 12:45.230
Shut up.

12:46.750 --> 12:47.270
Did you deliberately

12:47.270 --> 12:48.600
let Xia Xiaolan see you?

12:50.360 --> 12:51.240
I just wanted to see

12:51.240 --> 12:51.870
how my cousin

12:51.870 --> 12:53.030
is doing now.

12:53.720 --> 12:55.250
I missed her. Is that wrong?

12:55.870 --> 12:57.270
Why are you so worried?

12:58.310 --> 12:59.770
With this new face of mine,

13:00.150 --> 13:01.030
she didn't recognize me

13:01.030 --> 13:02.080
at all, did she?

13:05.480 --> 13:06.150
Xia Ziyu,

13:07.240 --> 13:08.970
you'd better behave yourself.

13:09.600 --> 13:10.320
Otherwise,

13:10.750 --> 13:11.750
I can send you away

13:12.270 --> 13:13.730
the same way I got you here.

13:22.600 --> 13:24.080
If Du Zhaohui and Xia Xiaolan

13:24.080 --> 13:26.210
collaborate and win the competition,

13:26.360 --> 13:27.750
he definitely won't hesitate

13:27.750 --> 13:29.440
to hand me over to Xia Xiaolan.

13:31.000 --> 13:33.000
I can't just sit here and wait to die.

13:35.550 --> 13:36.670
The clue Du Zhaohui gave

13:36.670 --> 13:37.630
is indeed true.

13:39.000 --> 13:40.460
That temp worker back then

13:41.840 --> 13:43.000
took a smuggling boat

13:43.000 --> 13:43.720
to Nanyang.

13:44.630 --> 13:45.720
That means...

13:46.270 --> 13:47.440
The smuggling ring

13:48.030 --> 13:49.300
must have silenced him

13:49.840 --> 13:51.440
to halt our investigations.

13:52.200 --> 13:53.150
You guessed it long ago,

13:53.150 --> 13:53.810
didn't you?

13:59.790 --> 14:00.920
I wondered about it.

14:01.870 --> 14:03.080
If I hadn't insisted

14:03.080 --> 14:04.760
on investigating the smuggling,

14:04.760 --> 14:05.430
then Shi Kai

14:06.150 --> 14:07.010
may not have...

14:09.000 --> 14:10.460
But I figured it out later.

14:11.320 --> 14:12.780
There are no "ifs" in life.

14:13.550 --> 14:14.680
And no turning back.

14:15.670 --> 14:17.480
Since we've come this far,

14:19.030 --> 14:20.960
we have to get to the bottom of this.

14:21.730 --> 14:25.490
[Zhiyuan Law Firm]

14:21.910 --> 14:23.440
Did you see the recent news?

14:23.640 --> 14:25.640
The police seized a smuggling boat.

14:25.720 --> 14:27.200
It was received here in Shengcheng.

14:27.200 --> 14:28.020
Ke Yixiong's men were behind it.

14:28.020 --> 14:30.390
Ke Yixiong started
working for Liu Tianquan,

14:30.390 --> 14:32.510
and Liu Tianquan is working
for the Du family.

14:32.510 --> 14:33.310
The Du family.

14:34.080 --> 14:34.750
Nanyang.

14:35.440 --> 14:36.550
Smuggling...

14:38.600 --> 14:39.460
I have a friend.

14:39.670 --> 14:40.870
He used to be a sailor.

14:41.120 --> 14:42.850
He sailed in Nanyang for years.

14:43.460 --> 14:44.520
Why don't we ask him for help?

14:44.520 --> 14:45.120
No.

14:45.240 --> 14:47.000
This is a matter for the authorities.

14:47.000 --> 14:48.060
We have protocols.

14:48.300 --> 14:50.230
We can't let civilians take risks.

15:46.910 --> 15:47.840
You found him?

15:52.360 --> 15:53.550
Is he still alive?

16:00.790 --> 16:01.910
Alive.

16:08.390 --> 16:09.320
Alive...

16:41.910 --> 16:43.310
This is his handwriting.

16:46.080 --> 16:47.240
I'm sure of it.

16:52.630 --> 16:54.680
What exactly happened?

16:58.360 --> 16:59.550
Over 20 years ago,

17:00.670 --> 17:01.750
he was set up

17:02.790 --> 17:05.400
and forced to flee to Gangdao.

17:23.240 --> 17:24.069
I'm fine now.

17:25.000 --> 17:27.000
I've thought of worse outcomes.

17:28.850 --> 17:29.780
Having news

17:30.000 --> 17:32.000
is better than having no news at all.

17:35.160 --> 17:35.880
Really?

17:38.550 --> 17:40.070
Actually, on my way back,

17:40.920 --> 17:42.000
I kept hesitating.

17:43.200 --> 17:44.110
I didn't know if

17:44.880 --> 17:46.640
real bad news would be better

17:47.750 --> 17:49.550
than false hope.

17:54.480 --> 17:55.440
Forgive me.

17:55.920 --> 17:57.250
I didn't know what to do.

17:58.640 --> 17:59.960
In the end,

17:59.960 --> 18:01.220
I told you everything.

18:03.030 --> 18:04.440
I want to thank you.

18:05.550 --> 18:06.160
Really.

18:08.550 --> 18:10.590
At my age,

18:11.590 --> 18:14.050
I've been through
all sorts of ups and downs.

18:15.070 --> 18:17.070
I've survived sufferings

18:17.870 --> 18:19.470
that others haven't tasted.

18:21.200 --> 18:22.230
I've hoped,

18:23.160 --> 18:24.070
longed,

18:25.370 --> 18:26.370
and waited.

18:28.590 --> 18:29.920
It's been over 20 years.

18:31.440 --> 18:32.470
In my heart,

18:33.400 --> 18:35.960
I've rehearsed
this scenario so many times.

18:40.200 --> 18:42.200
Now that there's finally a result,

18:43.830 --> 18:44.750
somehow,

18:46.790 --> 18:49.450
I just don't have the energy
to be upset anymore.

18:53.830 --> 18:54.700
Xiaolan,

18:55.920 --> 18:57.110
you are still young.

18:59.720 --> 19:01.180
While you can still laugh,

19:02.480 --> 19:03.350
cry,

19:04.200 --> 19:05.110
love,

19:06.590 --> 19:07.510
and ache,

19:09.680 --> 19:11.540
experience it all to the fullest.

19:14.840 --> 19:16.840
I... I'm tired.

19:18.590 --> 19:19.990
I want to rest for a while.

19:21.880 --> 19:23.640
Remember to close the door for me

19:23.640 --> 19:24.830
when you leave.

19:25.920 --> 19:26.850
Okay, Granny Yu.

19:27.550 --> 19:28.270
Get some rest.

19:28.270 --> 19:28.720
Okay.

19:40.200 --> 19:41.200
I'll be going now.

20:15.510 --> 20:16.200
How is it?

20:16.680 --> 20:17.790
Is Granny Yu okay?

20:18.920 --> 20:20.240
I don't know if

20:20.240 --> 20:21.240
she's okay or not.

20:22.750 --> 20:24.310
Granny Yu must be tired.

20:24.440 --> 20:26.370
You should get some rest soon, too.

20:26.420 --> 20:27.640
Oh, Mr. Mao said that

20:27.640 --> 20:29.770
you're going to Jiangcheng tomorrow.

20:30.590 --> 20:31.030
Yes.

20:31.550 --> 20:31.960
Okay.

20:32.960 --> 20:33.350
Mom.

20:33.510 --> 20:34.240
Don't worry.

20:34.790 --> 20:36.190
We're here for Granny Yu.

20:36.240 --> 20:37.100
She'll be fine.

20:37.510 --> 20:38.040
Let's go.

20:53.270 --> 20:54.730
While you can still laugh,

20:55.160 --> 20:56.000
cry,

20:57.070 --> 20:58.070
love,

20:58.550 --> 20:59.640
and ache,

21:00.510 --> 21:02.370
experience it all to the fullest.

21:03.210 --> 21:03.970
But...

21:04.920 --> 21:06.780
The happier you are when you love,

21:07.720 --> 21:09.640
the more painful the parting is.

21:11.400 --> 21:13.130
I don't want to go through that.

21:13.680 --> 21:16.750
And I don't want the people I love
to go through it either.

21:16.750 --> 21:18.110
Yet, I'm powerless.

21:47.870 --> 21:48.680
Why did I set

21:48.680 --> 21:49.940
an alarm for this time?

22:04.470 --> 22:05.600
Morning, Granny Yu.

22:06.590 --> 22:07.920
You're here early.

22:15.270 --> 22:15.640
Here.

22:16.750 --> 22:17.280
Morning.

22:17.310 --> 22:17.840
Morning.

22:21.720 --> 22:22.310
How is

22:22.590 --> 22:23.190
Granny Yu?

22:23.270 --> 22:24.130
Is she alright?

22:25.030 --> 22:25.880
I don't know.

22:29.200 --> 22:30.060
What about you?

22:30.590 --> 22:31.520
Are you alright?

22:32.000 --> 22:33.200
You came to the law firm yesterday.

22:33.200 --> 22:34.460
Why didn't you come in?

22:36.030 --> 22:37.000
I saw you and Jiang Yan

22:37.000 --> 22:37.750
discussing work,

22:37.750 --> 22:39.480
so I didn't go in to disturb you.

22:39.550 --> 22:40.070
Besides,

22:40.070 --> 22:40.750
I was also thinking about

22:40.750 --> 22:41.880
Granny Yu's matter.

22:43.070 --> 22:43.590
Look.

22:43.790 --> 22:45.550
Granny Yu went through such a huge ordeal,

22:45.550 --> 22:46.830
but she didn't collapse.

22:46.830 --> 22:48.160
We should learn from her

22:48.310 --> 22:49.640
and live our lives well.

22:49.720 --> 22:51.160
The things that trap us

22:51.480 --> 22:52.680
will all be resolved.

22:53.510 --> 22:54.030
Yes.

22:54.600 --> 22:56.080
But if we keep dawdling,

22:56.110 --> 22:56.680
we'll miss

22:56.680 --> 22:58.140
the flight to Jiangcheng.

22:58.640 --> 22:58.980
Let's go.

22:58.980 --> 23:00.110
Okay, I'll close the door.

23:00.110 --> 23:00.440
Okay.

23:05.880 --> 23:06.410
Let's go.

23:10.690 --> 23:14.770
[Jiangcheng]

23:15.140 --> 23:19.580
[Celebrating The Opening of The 6th Academic
Symposium on Modern Architectural Creation]

23:32.680 --> 23:33.540
Sorry, Ms. Xia.

23:34.550 --> 23:35.240
What's the matter?

23:35.240 --> 23:36.050
Why are you so nervous?

23:36.050 --> 23:37.790
It's my first time attending
this kind of event.

23:37.790 --> 23:38.750
I'm a bit excited.

23:38.750 --> 23:40.110
I feel like anyone I brush shoulders with

23:40.110 --> 23:41.110
could be a master.

23:42.650 --> 23:43.800
Mr. Mao is the

23:43.830 --> 23:45.090
greatest master here.

23:45.200 --> 23:46.240
You're already working for him.

23:46.240 --> 23:47.250
What else are you afraid of?

23:47.250 --> 23:48.240
I'm not like you, Ms. Xia.

23:48.240 --> 23:49.200
You have a solid background and

23:49.200 --> 23:50.880
graduated from Huaqing's
Architecture Department.

23:50.880 --> 23:52.270
I entered this field halfway.

23:52.270 --> 23:53.730
I really lack confidence.

23:57.190 --> 23:58.110
Mr. Mao.

23:58.130 --> 23:59.130
Professor Ning.

24:01.270 --> 24:02.680
It's truly rare.

24:03.070 --> 24:04.000
You are...

24:04.000 --> 24:04.550
Ms. Xia.

24:05.440 --> 24:06.110
Is this the master

24:06.110 --> 24:07.440
as renowned as Mr. Mao,

24:07.920 --> 24:09.240
known as "South Mao, North Ning,"

24:09.240 --> 24:10.570
Professor Ning Yanfan?

24:11.200 --> 24:11.680
Yes.

24:13.270 --> 24:14.110
I heard

24:14.270 --> 24:15.880
you recommended a

24:17.000 --> 24:18.240
promising junior.

24:19.160 --> 24:19.790
So,

24:20.200 --> 24:21.880
are you here

24:22.350 --> 24:24.270
to support your brilliant student

24:24.270 --> 24:25.440
in person?

24:26.240 --> 24:28.000
Her name is Xia Xiaolan.

24:28.110 --> 24:31.000
She graduated from the Huaqing
Department of Architecture.

24:31.000 --> 24:31.720
Xiaolan,

24:31.960 --> 24:32.640
come here.

24:33.070 --> 24:34.480
Let me introduce you.

24:34.680 --> 24:35.590
This is

24:35.680 --> 24:38.960
the renowned Professor Ning Yanfan,

24:39.590 --> 24:42.110
chairman of this symposium.

24:43.720 --> 24:44.510
Hello, Professor Ning.

24:44.510 --> 24:45.200
Hello.

24:45.220 --> 24:46.250
I am Xia Xiaolan.

24:46.590 --> 24:47.400
I am honored

24:47.400 --> 24:49.070
to attend this symposium.

24:49.400 --> 24:50.350
I will cherish

24:50.350 --> 24:51.410
this opportunity.

24:52.440 --> 24:55.270
Talent truly appears in every generation.

24:55.920 --> 24:56.960
So young,

24:57.440 --> 25:00.200
and a graduate of Huaqing Architecture.

25:01.030 --> 25:01.920
Mr. Mao,

25:02.350 --> 25:03.510
we are going to be

25:04.030 --> 25:06.310
pushed aside by the new wave.

25:06.440 --> 25:08.160
We are getting old.

25:08.880 --> 25:09.920
What a coincidence.

25:09.920 --> 25:10.830
I also graduated from

25:10.830 --> 25:12.160
Huaqing Architecture.

25:12.160 --> 25:13.400
How come I’ve never seen

25:13.400 --> 25:14.660
this junior at school?

25:15.140 --> 25:16.400
Which class were you in?

25:16.400 --> 25:17.800
I'm from the Class of '80.

25:18.070 --> 25:20.270
So you are a senior from the Class of '80.

25:20.590 --> 25:21.450
Hello, Senior.

25:21.720 --> 25:23.120
I'm from the Class of '88.

25:23.160 --> 25:25.110
So it's normal that you never saw me.

25:25.110 --> 25:26.350
Class of '88.

25:26.560 --> 25:28.000
So which design institute are you at,

25:28.000 --> 25:30.000
and what project are you working on?

25:30.200 --> 25:31.270
You must be deeply

25:31.270 --> 25:32.350
favored by Mr. Mao.

25:32.470 --> 25:33.480
Otherwise, why would he bring you

25:33.480 --> 25:34.540
to this symposium?

25:34.720 --> 25:35.240
Mr. Mao,

25:35.350 --> 25:36.550
aren't you being a bit

25:36.590 --> 25:38.120
too hasty in promoting her?

25:39.480 --> 25:40.410
Professor Ning,

25:41.310 --> 25:43.240
when did the rules change?

25:43.720 --> 25:45.270
Instead of their work,

25:45.550 --> 25:46.880
we're looking at seniority

25:46.880 --> 25:49.480
to decide who
gets to attend the symposium now?

25:50.390 --> 25:51.020
Say,

25:52.200 --> 25:53.650
who are you?

25:54.830 --> 25:57.290
Are you from the Architecture Association?

25:57.750 --> 25:59.270
My eyes are dim,

25:59.440 --> 26:00.900
I haven't seen you before.

26:02.690 --> 26:04.040
He is the deputy dean

26:04.070 --> 26:05.110
of Jiangcheng Design Institute,

26:05.110 --> 26:06.030
Nie Weiguo.

26:07.030 --> 26:07.750
Mr. Mao, a pleasure to meet you.

26:07.750 --> 26:09.750
I don't have time for your nonsense.

26:09.920 --> 26:10.920
I'm going to rest.

26:11.510 --> 26:12.110
Mr. Mao...

26:12.310 --> 26:12.960
Mr. Mao.

26:17.510 --> 26:18.370
Chairman Ning,

26:18.720 --> 26:20.070
we won't disturb you any longer.

26:20.070 --> 26:20.440
Okay.

26:20.790 --> 26:22.000
Go handle the paperwork.

26:22.000 --> 26:22.480
Okay.

26:25.270 --> 26:26.070
Nie.

26:26.280 --> 26:28.130
Watch your language.

26:28.790 --> 26:30.310
You are a deputy dean, after all.

26:30.310 --> 26:30.640
Right?

26:30.640 --> 26:31.680
Okay. Let's go.

26:31.700 --> 26:33.160
Professor Ning, let's go.

26:35.200 --> 26:36.920
Ms. Xia, you're just too dazzling.

26:36.920 --> 26:38.550
It really makes people jealous.

26:38.550 --> 26:40.030
He only thinks about stepping on others

26:40.030 --> 26:41.760
instead of improving himself.

26:42.000 --> 26:42.950
I think

26:43.000 --> 26:43.790
he'll spend his whole life

26:43.790 --> 26:45.120
watching others shine.

26:45.590 --> 26:47.320
But that is his turf, after all.

26:47.350 --> 26:48.880
For tomorrow's symposium,

26:49.070 --> 26:50.590
I bet he's already planned

26:50.590 --> 26:51.790
how to embarrass you.

26:52.350 --> 26:53.200
But I'm sure

26:53.720 --> 26:55.180
you're already prepared.

26:55.350 --> 26:57.030
I came to this symposium

26:57.030 --> 26:58.480
to network.

26:59.010 --> 27:00.210
As a newcomer,

27:00.240 --> 27:02.000
no one would take my speech seriously.

27:02.000 --> 27:03.030
I was just wondering

27:03.030 --> 27:04.890
how to get everyone's attention.

27:05.200 --> 27:06.440
You really are

27:06.440 --> 27:07.700
always in combat mode.

27:07.920 --> 27:09.720
But don't push yourself too hard.

27:09.720 --> 27:10.720
You need to relax.

27:10.920 --> 27:12.880
I'm actually quite lucky

27:13.110 --> 27:14.880
to have Mr. Mao recommend me.

27:15.270 --> 27:15.830
But Mr. Mao

27:15.830 --> 27:17.000
can only protect me for so long.

27:17.000 --> 27:18.600
He can't protect me forever.

27:18.790 --> 27:19.830
To win,

27:20.270 --> 27:21.590
you can't just rely on luck.

27:21.590 --> 27:23.030
You have to rely on yourself.

27:23.030 --> 27:23.830
I have to fight

27:23.850 --> 27:24.980
this battle myself.

27:25.640 --> 27:26.170
Alright.

27:26.350 --> 27:27.610
I'm going to get ready.

27:28.550 --> 27:29.150
Good luck.

27:29.830 --> 27:30.680
Okay. Bye.

27:34.990 --> 27:38.350
[Day 1 of Symposium]

27:50.650 --> 27:53.560
[The 6th Academic Symposium on
Modern Architectural Creation]

28:02.350 --> 28:02.790
You're here.

28:02.790 --> 28:03.590
The seats are inside.

28:03.590 --> 28:04.160
Let's go.

28:04.510 --> 28:05.000
Nie.

28:05.720 --> 28:06.510
Xing.

28:07.000 --> 28:07.880
Long time no see.

28:07.880 --> 28:08.640
Have a seat.

28:09.030 --> 28:09.480
Xing.

28:09.830 --> 28:10.590
Have a seat.

28:10.610 --> 28:11.040
Okay.

28:11.350 --> 28:13.310
Did you come by train?

28:13.310 --> 28:13.830
Or...

28:13.830 --> 28:14.760
I took the train.

28:16.440 --> 28:17.400
I think the scale this time

28:17.400 --> 28:18.600
is quite impressive.

28:18.960 --> 28:19.440
Yes.

28:19.750 --> 28:21.200
Look at the turnout.

28:21.790 --> 28:22.200
Right?

28:22.310 --> 28:22.910
Quite a crowd.

28:22.910 --> 28:23.440
Exactly.

28:24.480 --> 28:25.000
Yeah.

28:26.220 --> 28:26.610
Yeah.

28:26.640 --> 28:28.040
There are so many people.

28:35.000 --> 28:35.440
Nie,

28:35.920 --> 28:36.750
as seniors,

28:37.220 --> 28:38.350
we should show some restraint

28:38.350 --> 28:39.480
and leave it at that.

28:40.960 --> 28:41.510
Xing,

28:42.160 --> 28:43.550
this is

28:44.000 --> 28:46.310
a national creation symposium.

28:46.310 --> 28:46.750
Right?

28:47.640 --> 28:48.680
So does that mean

28:48.800 --> 28:50.560
people with no qualifications

28:50.590 --> 28:52.310
can attend just because

28:52.310 --> 28:53.840
a senior recommended them?

28:53.960 --> 28:55.790
If that's the case,

28:56.480 --> 28:58.440
can those country bumpkins building pigsties

28:58.440 --> 28:59.900
and any Tom, Dick, or Harry

29:00.720 --> 29:01.310
also

29:01.480 --> 29:03.140
call themselves architects?

29:03.160 --> 29:04.220
Alright, alright.

29:04.560 --> 29:05.030
That's enough.

29:05.030 --> 29:06.430
Let's start the meeting.

29:09.790 --> 29:10.520
You're here.

29:11.070 --> 29:12.440
Are you meeting a client?

29:12.440 --> 29:13.570
Sorry, I'll just...

29:13.570 --> 29:14.170
It's fine.

29:15.030 --> 29:15.960
This is the seaman friend

29:15.960 --> 29:17.030
I told you about.

29:20.920 --> 29:21.580
Zhou Cheng.

29:21.590 --> 29:22.650
I told you already.

29:22.830 --> 29:23.480
Um,

29:23.880 --> 29:25.540
you must be Prosecutor Jiang.

29:26.680 --> 29:27.640
I'm Pan Baohua.

29:27.830 --> 29:29.360
People usually call me San.

29:29.550 --> 29:30.240
Today,

29:30.510 --> 29:32.350
I came to see you myself.

29:35.590 --> 29:36.550
Nice to meet you, San.

29:36.550 --> 29:36.920
Hello.

29:36.920 --> 29:39.520
I'm Jiang Yan from
Shengcheng Procuratorate.

29:53.190 --> 29:55.070
It's been years since
Northern Ning and Southern Mao

29:55.070 --> 29:56.030
sat together again.

29:56.030 --> 29:56.480
Yes.

29:56.640 --> 29:57.680
Mr. Mao hasn't attended

29:57.680 --> 29:58.310
industry events

29:58.310 --> 29:59.200
in years.

30:09.200 --> 30:09.920
The 6th

30:10.000 --> 30:12.200
Symposium on Modern Architectural Creation

30:12.200 --> 30:14.070
officially begins.

30:19.350 --> 30:21.030
Reshaping the creative environment,

30:21.030 --> 30:22.550
flourishing architectural creation,

30:22.550 --> 30:24.010
and correcting monotony.

30:24.240 --> 30:24.880
Next,

30:24.880 --> 30:25.550
we invite

30:25.640 --> 30:27.400
the chairman of this symposium,

30:27.400 --> 30:28.960
Professor Ning Yanfan, to speak.

30:28.960 --> 30:30.090
Please welcome him.

30:35.070 --> 30:35.750
Comrades,

30:36.640 --> 30:39.310
we are gathered

30:40.030 --> 30:41.880
here today.

30:42.480 --> 30:43.310
Professor Ning,

30:43.310 --> 30:44.110
I

30:44.510 --> 30:46.240
have a request.

30:46.760 --> 30:47.350
I wonder if you would

30:47.350 --> 30:49.080
be willing to hear me out first.

30:49.240 --> 30:49.830
Nie,

30:50.750 --> 30:52.210
you have something to say?

30:52.830 --> 30:53.880
Don't rush.

30:54.110 --> 30:56.200
The symposium lasts for 3 days.

30:56.750 --> 30:57.680
Professor Ning,

30:57.880 --> 30:59.510
the symposium is indeed 3 days long.

30:59.510 --> 31:01.070
But by the time I speak,

31:01.200 --> 31:01.930
this meeting

31:01.960 --> 31:02.960
will be half over.

31:03.440 --> 31:04.240
I think that

31:04.790 --> 31:06.390
before we start the meeting,

31:06.550 --> 31:08.440
we should consider verifying

31:08.590 --> 31:10.720
the qualifications of the attendees.

31:12.110 --> 31:14.510
Shouldn't they at least belong to

31:14.790 --> 31:15.790
a basic work unit?

31:16.720 --> 31:17.480
Today,

31:17.530 --> 31:18.480
some attendees

31:18.510 --> 31:19.910
not only lack a work unit,

31:20.030 --> 31:21.920
but also have no representative works.

31:21.920 --> 31:22.750
They don't even

31:22.750 --> 31:24.030
have a single research paper

31:24.030 --> 31:24.830
to their name.

31:25.110 --> 31:26.880
Wouldn't their attendance

31:27.310 --> 31:27.920
make this symposium

31:27.920 --> 31:28.880
a bit of a joke?

31:33.480 --> 31:34.110
Nie,

31:35.030 --> 31:37.030
the work unit, research papers,

31:37.030 --> 31:38.610
and seniority you mentioned

31:38.610 --> 31:40.650
are not hard criteria

31:40.680 --> 31:41.810
for this symposium.

31:42.550 --> 31:44.080
The purpose of this meeting

31:44.510 --> 31:47.480
is to explore new architectural styles

31:47.960 --> 31:49.290
and break conventions.

31:50.070 --> 31:52.720
As long as their
professional level is sufficient,

31:52.720 --> 31:53.920
we welcome them

31:53.920 --> 31:55.380
to exchange ideas with us.

31:55.640 --> 31:56.640
We are happy

31:57.240 --> 31:59.070
to provide the younger generation

31:59.070 --> 32:00.200
with an opportunity

32:00.200 --> 32:02.590
to showcase their talent.

32:10.960 --> 32:12.290
Hello, Professor Ning.

32:13.790 --> 32:15.400
Deputy Dean Nie

32:16.200 --> 32:17.600
must be talking about me.

32:18.510 --> 32:19.880
Deputy Dean Nie thinks

32:20.310 --> 32:22.310
that I am a newcomer with no position

32:22.480 --> 32:24.110
or representative works.

32:24.400 --> 32:25.750
My attendance here

32:26.240 --> 32:27.000
lowers the standard

32:27.000 --> 32:28.400
of the entire symposium.

32:29.680 --> 32:30.640
He also thinks that

32:30.640 --> 32:33.100
Mr. Mao's recommendation for my attendance

32:33.160 --> 32:34.020
is favoritism.

32:36.680 --> 32:38.720
Then do you think

32:39.000 --> 32:40.640
you are qualified to be here?

32:43.270 --> 32:44.000
To be honest,

32:44.480 --> 32:46.590
when I first received the invitation,

32:46.590 --> 32:48.310
I did hesitate.

32:48.960 --> 32:50.640
I am just a fresh graduate

32:50.640 --> 32:52.160
from the architecture department.

32:52.160 --> 32:53.890
How do I deserve to participate

32:53.920 --> 32:55.510
in the discussion with all the seniors

32:55.510 --> 32:56.680
present here?

32:58.030 --> 32:58.830
But...

32:59.720 --> 33:00.790
I really didn't want to

33:00.790 --> 33:02.270
miss this chance to learn.

33:02.640 --> 33:03.900
So I shamelessly came.

33:06.550 --> 33:07.720
Deputy Dean Nie

33:08.000 --> 33:10.000
may question my eligibility to attend,

33:10.000 --> 33:11.200
but I'm not offended.

33:11.310 --> 33:12.440
Because you are my

33:12.480 --> 33:14.340
senior from the same department.

33:14.440 --> 33:15.480
Whatever you do

33:15.570 --> 33:16.830
is out of care for me.

33:18.310 --> 33:19.070
Senior Nie,

33:20.070 --> 33:20.870
rest assured,

33:21.160 --> 33:22.480
I won't let you down.

33:24.400 --> 33:25.400
I see the work Mr. Mao

33:25.400 --> 33:27.160
submitted for you is

33:27.550 --> 33:29.310
the interior design plan

33:29.550 --> 33:31.350
for Shengcheng's Haihua Hotel.

33:32.030 --> 33:32.830
Alright then.

33:32.920 --> 33:34.720
Come up and tell us about it.

33:35.310 --> 33:36.510
Let everyone see

33:36.920 --> 33:38.640
if you are qualified

33:38.880 --> 33:40.480
to be recommended by Mr. Mao.

33:42.550 --> 33:43.480
Professor Ning.

33:44.750 --> 33:45.790
As far as I know,

33:46.030 --> 33:47.880
Haihua Hotel

33:49.000 --> 33:50.920
is Mr. Mao Kangshan's work.

33:51.680 --> 33:52.350
I think

33:52.850 --> 33:54.030
all the colleagues present here

33:54.030 --> 33:55.160
have heard about it.

33:55.830 --> 33:56.430
Of course,

33:56.960 --> 33:57.640
Mr. Mao's

33:57.640 --> 33:58.790
eagerness to recommend his

33:58.790 --> 33:59.510
favourite student

33:59.510 --> 34:00.640
is understandable.

34:00.830 --> 34:01.480
However,

34:01.640 --> 34:02.920
isn't it a bit

34:02.960 --> 34:04.480
inappropriate to use his own work

34:04.480 --> 34:05.440
to keep up an appearance

34:05.440 --> 34:06.480
for his student?

34:08.400 --> 34:10.840
Nie, your news is outdated.

34:12.110 --> 34:13.510
Haihua Hotel

34:13.739 --> 34:15.530
was indeed designed by me.

34:16.170 --> 34:18.730
But that was only the main structure.

34:19.190 --> 34:21.840
The specific interior design plan

34:22.190 --> 34:23.960
was rejected

34:23.960 --> 34:25.190
by the investors.

34:25.880 --> 34:27.710
Later, Xia Xiaolan took over.

34:28.630 --> 34:30.760
I recommended her for

34:30.760 --> 34:32.030
this symposium

34:33.110 --> 34:34.880
mainly because her work

34:35.710 --> 34:37.960
has a brilliant idea.

34:39.360 --> 34:40.070
Mr. Mao,

34:40.510 --> 34:42.670
the brilliant idea you mentioned

34:43.070 --> 34:46.480
must be the infinity pool.

34:47.070 --> 34:48.150
As for the details,

34:48.440 --> 34:50.320
let Xia Xiaolan explain them.

34:51.230 --> 34:51.760
Alright.

34:52.150 --> 34:52.630
Xia.

34:58.280 --> 34:59.140
She's so young.

35:09.280 --> 35:10.210
Hello everyone.

35:10.400 --> 35:11.320
I am Xia Xiaolan

35:11.320 --> 35:13.360
from Shengcheng's Yuanhui Decoration.

35:13.360 --> 35:13.920
Next,

35:13.940 --> 35:15.600
I will give a brief explanation

35:15.600 --> 35:16.440
of the interior design plan

35:16.440 --> 35:17.760
for Haihua Hotel.

35:18.920 --> 35:20.520
I've never seen this before.

35:21.450 --> 35:23.250
And now she's the first speaker.

35:23.440 --> 35:24.760
Isn't that ridiculous?

35:24.760 --> 35:25.550
Nie Weiguo

35:25.550 --> 35:26.760
was too eager

35:26.780 --> 35:27.710
to embarrass her.

35:27.710 --> 35:28.510
Yes, exactly.

35:28.960 --> 35:30.150
Look at this. It's not bad.

35:30.150 --> 35:31.710
I've never seen this before.

35:31.710 --> 35:32.230
San,

35:32.800 --> 35:34.060
I admire your courage.

35:34.630 --> 35:35.550
But my attitude and stance

35:35.550 --> 35:36.510
will never change.

35:36.510 --> 35:37.190
I disagree.

35:40.070 --> 35:40.860
Prosecutor Jiang,

35:40.860 --> 35:41.400
why don't you...

35:41.400 --> 35:42.460
San, stop talking.

35:42.630 --> 35:44.360
Zhou Cheng, I'm leaving first.

35:53.670 --> 35:55.920
As a window to the outside world

35:55.920 --> 35:57.150
for Reform and Opening-Up,

35:57.150 --> 35:58.510
Shengcheng plays a crucial role

35:58.510 --> 36:00.000
as a pioneer.

36:00.480 --> 36:01.680
In the next few years,

36:01.760 --> 36:03.600
Shengcheng will develop rapidly

36:03.600 --> 36:05.200
into a modern

36:05.230 --> 36:06.830
international metropolis.

36:06.960 --> 36:07.960
For Haihua Hotel

36:08.000 --> 36:09.510
to stand out

36:09.510 --> 36:10.590
among all the other hotels,

36:10.590 --> 36:11.800
it needs a gimmick.

36:13.110 --> 36:15.110
As mentioned in my design proposal,

36:15.150 --> 36:16.480
the infinity pool

36:16.560 --> 36:18.520
will make it a unique scenic spot

36:18.550 --> 36:20.590
in Shengcheng.

36:22.000 --> 36:22.630
Although

36:22.800 --> 36:23.880
it's a renovation plan...

36:23.880 --> 36:24.510
You see,

36:24.710 --> 36:25.510
it already involves

36:25.510 --> 36:27.320
modifying the entire main structure.

36:27.320 --> 36:28.880
Calling it an architectural work

36:28.880 --> 36:30.540
would not be an exaggeration.

36:31.030 --> 36:31.590
I know

36:32.550 --> 36:33.590
many people think that

36:33.590 --> 36:34.960
an infinity pool

36:35.230 --> 36:37.110
is impossible.

36:37.850 --> 36:38.520
However,

36:38.550 --> 36:39.360
we have already conducted

36:39.360 --> 36:40.440
rigorous data calculations

36:40.440 --> 36:42.400
and model tests

36:42.590 --> 36:44.000
on this design proposal,

36:44.510 --> 36:44.970
proving

36:45.110 --> 36:47.030
that this plan is feasible.

36:48.150 --> 36:49.130
A budget of 30 million.

36:49.130 --> 36:50.260
It's a huge project.

36:50.550 --> 36:51.030
Yes.

36:51.400 --> 36:52.440
If a 30 million project

36:52.440 --> 36:53.320
isn't considered an established work,

36:53.320 --> 36:54.190
then we aren't qualified

36:54.190 --> 36:55.110
to be sitting here, either.

36:55.110 --> 36:55.710
Exactly.

36:55.800 --> 36:56.340
That concludes

36:56.340 --> 36:58.200
my design concept presentation.

36:58.480 --> 36:59.680
Thank you, everyone.

37:10.080 --> 37:11.450
A mock-up

37:11.480 --> 37:13.550
is different from actual construction.

37:13.550 --> 37:14.960
So, Junior Xia,

37:15.320 --> 37:15.800
basically,

37:15.800 --> 37:17.030
your design remains

37:17.030 --> 37:18.230
merely on paper for now.

37:18.230 --> 37:20.160
It hasn't been adopted yet, has it?

37:21.450 --> 37:23.080
Senior Nie,

37:23.110 --> 37:23.960
you really are

37:23.980 --> 37:25.840
very concerned about my matters.

37:26.400 --> 37:27.550
Haihua Hotel

37:27.580 --> 37:29.600
is currently under intense construction.

37:29.600 --> 37:30.710
By the end of next year at the latest,

37:30.710 --> 37:32.840
it will officially open for business.

37:33.230 --> 37:34.000
If you

37:34.000 --> 37:35.150
still have doubts,

37:35.410 --> 37:36.450
why don't you come

37:36.480 --> 37:37.920
and stay for a few days then?

37:37.920 --> 37:39.150
Let me know in advance,

37:39.150 --> 37:40.550
and I'll see if I can find someone

37:40.550 --> 37:41.760
to get you a discount.

37:45.320 --> 37:45.920
Thank you.

37:48.760 --> 37:50.630
Everyone, pause for a moment.

37:51.280 --> 37:54.320
Is everyone satisfied with

37:55.670 --> 37:56.960
Comrade Xia's answers?

37:56.960 --> 37:59.510
Satisfied. Very satisfied.

38:04.190 --> 38:04.920
Now,

38:05.650 --> 38:07.060
does anyone still doubt

38:07.480 --> 38:08.480
that this plan

38:08.920 --> 38:10.880
was designed by Xia?

38:11.200 --> 38:12.680
No doubts.

38:12.710 --> 38:14.230
This design is very novel

38:14.440 --> 38:15.570
and inspiring to us.

38:15.880 --> 38:16.400
Yes.

38:16.760 --> 38:17.840
I think this plan

38:18.000 --> 38:19.130
is completely fine!

38:20.280 --> 38:21.080
That's right.

38:21.670 --> 38:22.440
Nie,

38:23.400 --> 38:24.230
tell us.

38:25.030 --> 38:26.000
Mr. Mao

38:26.400 --> 38:28.960
recommended Xia Xiaolan for the symposium.

38:29.710 --> 38:31.320
Is she qualified?

38:33.840 --> 38:34.770
Professor Ning,

38:35.030 --> 38:36.630
in terms of seniority,

38:36.800 --> 38:37.480
Junior Xia

38:37.500 --> 38:39.100
is certainly not qualified.

38:39.280 --> 38:39.810
However,

38:40.400 --> 38:42.400
with Mr. Mao's personal recommendation,

38:42.400 --> 38:43.630
and Junior Xia's

38:43.760 --> 38:45.150
innovative work,

38:45.370 --> 38:46.550
she is certainly qualified,

38:46.550 --> 38:47.030
right?

38:56.480 --> 38:58.480
Of course, I won a complete victory.

38:58.840 --> 39:00.520
A buffoon like him

39:00.550 --> 39:01.360
will only become

39:01.360 --> 39:03.490
a stepping stone on my path to success.

39:04.800 --> 39:05.800
Then in 2 more days,

39:05.800 --> 39:07.260
you should be back, right?

39:08.150 --> 39:08.800
Why?

39:09.150 --> 39:11.350
Does a day apart feel like 3 years to you?

39:15.630 --> 39:17.030
I feel like recent events

39:17.590 --> 39:19.120
have all happened in a rush.

39:19.880 --> 39:21.340
Buying land and building,

39:21.630 --> 39:23.230
managing Golden Sands Pool,

39:23.770 --> 39:25.500
and finding Granny Yu's son...

39:25.810 --> 39:26.670
It's been a rollercoaster.

39:26.670 --> 39:28.710
Mr. Zhou, since when did you start

39:28.710 --> 39:30.110
getting so sentimental?

39:30.770 --> 39:31.230
Alright.

39:31.230 --> 39:32.430
I'll be back in 2 days.

39:33.530 --> 39:34.730
Zhenzhu's birthday

39:34.760 --> 39:36.090
is also in 2 days, right?

39:36.150 --> 39:36.680
Perfect.

39:36.920 --> 39:38.580
Let's get everyone together.

39:38.840 --> 39:39.230
Okay.

39:39.880 --> 39:40.880
Whatever you say.

39:41.590 --> 39:42.790
Alright, I have to go.

39:42.920 --> 39:44.510
I need to keep preparing.

39:46.070 --> 39:46.510
Bye.

39:46.880 --> 39:47.360
Bye.

39:54.190 --> 39:55.480
How could he possibly

39:56.030 --> 39:56.880
be blind to my

39:56.880 --> 39:58.010
strange behaviors?

39:59.150 --> 40:00.070
But...

40:00.960 --> 40:02.320
How should I tell him?

40:05.150 --> 40:05.710
Xiaolan,

40:07.280 --> 40:07.840
do you have a

40:07.840 --> 40:09.240
secret you can't tell me?

40:11.200 --> 40:14.440
[Day 2 of Symposium]

40:17.450 --> 40:21.540
♪ The sunlight fell on me ♪

40:22.590 --> 40:25.030
♪ Sometimes I want to go crazy ♪

40:25.050 --> 40:28.830
♪ Once you've made up your mind, be brave ♪

40:29.150 --> 40:31.710
♪ And head to the distant place ♪

40:32.700 --> 40:35.080
♪ There are laughter and tears ♪

40:36.010 --> 40:38.620
♪ There's joy and sorrow ♪

40:39.290 --> 40:43.690
♪ But this is life ♪

40:44.180 --> 40:47.700
♪ Why don't we move forward
and never look back? ♪

40:47.720 --> 40:51.020
♪ Even if our youthful ambitions
are not fulfilled yet ♪

40:51.160 --> 40:54.060
♪ We never give up ♪

40:54.700 --> 40:57.830
♪ We can rely on each other on the road,
and that's enough ♪

40:57.850 --> 41:01.070
♪ Just walk forward and never look back ♪

41:01.280 --> 41:04.500
♪ Don't look down on us youths
whose great ambitions are yet fulfilled ♪

41:01.550 --> 41:02.550
Is everyone ready?

41:02.030 --> 41:05.710
[Day 3 of Symposium]

41:02.800 --> 41:03.550
Look here.

41:03.760 --> 41:04.870
Let's take a group photo.

41:04.870 --> 41:07.810
♪ The future will be amazing ♪

41:05.670 --> 41:06.840
Come on, look here.

41:07.150 --> 41:09.400
3, 2, 1.

41:08.500 --> 41:14.890
♪ That'd be enough ♪

41:14.320 --> 41:14.920
Mr. Mao.

41:15.480 --> 41:18.080
A great teacher
produces a brilliant student.

41:18.230 --> 41:19.670
Your student, Xia, is really impressive.

41:19.670 --> 41:20.320
Professor Ning,

41:20.320 --> 41:21.520
it's all thanks to you

41:21.760 --> 41:23.590
for initiating this symposium.

41:28.030 --> 41:28.690
Junior Xia.

41:31.480 --> 41:33.320
It's your first time at the symposium,

41:33.320 --> 41:34.880
and you've already
gained recognition within the industry.

41:34.880 --> 41:35.340
Not bad.

41:36.070 --> 41:37.130
Congratulations.

41:38.110 --> 41:39.510
I have to thank you, Senior Nie,

41:39.510 --> 41:40.770
for setting the stage.

41:41.840 --> 41:43.370
I will remember this favor.

41:43.840 --> 41:44.300
See you.

41:44.320 --> 41:44.760
See you.
